flowchart TD
    Cell[Blueprint cell] --> Retr[Chroma retrieval]
    Retr --> SME[SME propose_items 2x]
    SME --> IWS[IWS cleanup]
    IWS --> LOA[LOA verify_alignment]
    LOA -->|aligned| Ground[Grounding verify]
    LOA -->|misaligned| Realign[LOA suggest_realignment]
    Realign --> LOA2[LOA re-verify]
    LOA2 -->|aligned| Ground
    LOA2 -->|misaligned| Rej1[reject]
    Ground -->|grounded| Accept[accept]
    Ground -->|not grounded| Rej2[reject]
    Accept --> CP2[Checkpoint 2]
